Package se.sics.tasim.props

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveOrders
    ActiveOrders contains information about active orders.
    AdminContent
    AdminContent is used for administrative communication with the server.
    Alert
    Alert is used for sending administrative messages to the user behind external agents.
    BankStatus
    BankStatus contains information about a participants bank account, recent penalties, and recent denied deliveries.
    BOMBundle
    BOMBundle contains information about which products that can be produced and which components that are needed for each product.
    ComponentCatalog
    ComponentCatalog contains information about which components that are available and which supplier(s) that are producing them.
    DeliveryNotice
    DeliveryNotice contains information about a set of deliveries made between two parts.
    DeliverySchedule
    DeliverySchedule contains information about deliveries to make.
    FactoryStatus
    FactoryStatus is an InventoryStatus extended with information about factory utilization.
    InventoryStatus
    InventoryStatus contains information about the quantity of products in an inventory.
    MarketReport
    MarketReport contains information about the supply and customer demand in the market during a period of time.
    OfferBundle
    OfferBundle contains an ordered set of offers.
    OrderBundle
    OrderBundle contains an set of orders.
    Ping
    Ping is used to verify the liveness of agent connections
    PriceReport
    PriceReport contains information about the price interval of ordered products.
    ProductionSchedule
    ProductionSchedule contains information about production to perform.
    RFQBundle
    RFQBundle contains an ordered set of requests for quotes.
    SCMInfo
    SCMInfo is used to generate transport contexts for communication with SCM servers.
    ServerConfig
    ServerConfig contains the server configuration for a game/simulation instance.
    SimpleContent
    SimpleContent is an abstract base class for parameterized messages.
    SimulationStatus
    SimulationStatus contains in game / simulation status.
    StartInfo
    StartInfo holds information about a game / simulation.
